      ],
      "parameters": {
        "text": "=You are an excellent palm reader.\n\nThe image sent is a palm image.\nIf it cannot be identified as a palm, output:\n【Unable to identify the image as a palm】\nDo not perform any of the following processing.\n\nIf the image is identified as a palm, provide the following output based on palm reading.\n\nNo reply to me is required.\n\nOutput content:\n～For the first session, I will tell your fortune based on your palm～\n【Life Line】 - (Score out of 10)\n【Heart Line】 - (Score out of 10)\n【Head Line】 - (Score out of 10)\n【Fate Line】 - (Score out of 10)\n【Overall Fortune】Provide overall advice based on the palm reading within 150 characters.",
