        "height": 608,
        "content": "## AI Comparison Analysis\n\nGoogle Gemini Vision model performs comparative analysis\nbetween current and previous palm images.\n\nThe model:\n- Detects palm presence\n- Compares lines, dryness, and color tone\n- Generates non-medical health insights (≤200 characters)\n\nNo medical diagnosis is provided.\n"
